;;; Terminal

Term colors: Black DarkRed DarkGreen Yellow DarkBlue Purple DarkCyan LightGrey
Term colors: DarkGrey LightRed LightGreen MutedYellow LightBlue Magenta Cyan White

;;; Links
Terminal           -> Normal
LineNrAbove        -> LineNr
LineNrBelow        -> LineNr
CurSearch          -> Search
CursorLineFold     -> CursorLine
CursorLineSign     -> CursorLine
EndOfBuffer        -> NonText
ErrorMsg           -> Error
Tag                -> Special
Operator           -> Statement
MessageWindow      -> Pmenu
PopupNotification  -> Todo


